    "long_instructions": "### Create Version 1\r\n\r\n**Do This:**\r\n- Choose one of the moods you described in your Activity Guide for you GIF.\r\n- Create a sequence of sounds that go with that mood and put it under `when run`. **Your sounds must last at least 6 measures!**\r\n- Use `1 triggered immediately` to code one sound effect that goes with your GIF.\r\n\r\nWhen you are finished, you should have one backtrack underneath the `when run` block and a `trigger` block with a sound effect. Here is an example of what this could look like\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/38cbdf49784908ebdb36e8f93456cfea-image-1745527719822.png)",
